snippet.title: THE BUNKER - Gameplay Trailer (2016)
snippet.description:
The first look at gameplay in The Bunker - A completely live action psychological horror. Starring Adam Brown (The Hobbit) and Sarah Greene (Penny Dreadful)

Pre-purchase now on Green Man Gaming - https://www.greenmangaming.com/games/the-bunker/

Developed by Splendy Games and Wales Interactive
Published by Green Man Gaming Publishing (PC) and Wales Interactive (Console)
